		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>How did the Internet change the everyday work of a security researcher?</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Aryeh Goretsky and David Harley talk to Sabrina Pagnotta about the internet's impact on security research.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2015-05-15 10:50:54">15 May 2015 - 10:50AM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>	

            <div class="content">
                <div class="social-wrapper" id="social-sharer">
